NAME

    HEP::Names::LaTeX - formats plain names of high energy physics (HEP)
    particles to LaTeX

VERSION

    version 0.01

SYNOPSIS

            use HEP::Names::LaTeX qw( particle_to_latex );
            use HEP::MCNS qw( particle_name );
            my $bplus_name_latex = particle_to_latex( $bplus_name );
            my $bzero_name_latex = particle_to_latex( particle_name( 511 ) );

DESCRIPTION

    Converts plain HEP particle names to nice LaTeX format. For now only
    one raw particle name format is implemented, namely that of HEP::MCNS.

FUNCTIONS

 particle_to_latex

    takes particle names and formats to LaTeX

